Comment: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:08.64,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Opening Skit ===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:08.64,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Tomari-chan, we've really become a great duo, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.98,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it's been quite a while since
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:14.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I became a main personality alongside you, Kanon-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:18.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,At first, I really worried about what we should talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I remember you asking me if I was enjoying school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I remember clearly how you told me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,that you were having fun back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:35.42,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Of course, even now, I find school, school idols, and this radio show very enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:40.12,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I can really tell how much you're enjoying this show, Tomari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:43.38,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,After all, we're always facing each other like this during recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:46.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Yes, I can see your expressions very clearly, Kanon-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:50.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Laughing, being troubled, being surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:54.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,You're so expressive that I never get tired of watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When you put it like that, it makes me feel like I don't have much of a "senpai" vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:03.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't you have any thoughts like, "She's so reliable" or "She's so sharp"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:06.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's that difficult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:08.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.34,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Of course I rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was getting a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:21.70,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Chi-chan once told me that I might act a bit childish on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.12,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:29.90,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Since my way of talking is quite detached, you act that way on purpose to liven things up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.59,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:35.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I guess there's a bit of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:36.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:42.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I think the main reason is that I really trust you, Tomari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You're always so on top of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:52.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your talk and timekeeping are perfect, so I think I've ended up depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's not very good of me as your senior, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No, it allows me to see a side of you that you don't show on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and that honestly makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Tomari-chan, you're such a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:12.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Let's keep delivering a fun radio show together from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.85,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now, let's get today's recording started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:17.53,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.80,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Suggestion Box ===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's time for the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Suggestion Box, where we read your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:44.87,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This is the Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Lunchtime Broadcasting Station, Lieraji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Now, everyone say it with us! One, two... Suggestion Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let's get right into the emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,First, we have one from Liella name: Popcorn Who Wanted to Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I attended the 7th Live performance in Kanagawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.72,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was truly a blast."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:08.12,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We got to see the solo songs for the first time, and Kanon-chan's 'Over Over' was especially hype!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:13.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Kanon-chan has always struggled with her feelings toward singing, so seeing her perform so happily..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:19.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It made me emotional realizing she reaffirmed her love for it through Season 3 of the anime."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:23.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Her energy during the call-and-response really took my excitement to the max!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next, we have one from Liella name: Mattsukutsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.02,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.02,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Kanon-chan's 'Over Over' was so exciting!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:38.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I only realized this after seeing it live, but isn't that song incredibly difficult to sing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.62,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing Kanon-chan running around the stage with so much energy made me so happy,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:47.04,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but I also felt like she was singing at full power the entire time."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I really felt like that song requires an immense amount of energy to pull off."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.66,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.70,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.24,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The solo songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Man, they were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.25,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:58.89,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm just so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Regarding 'Over Over'...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:12.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Kanon's past solo songs have had a lot of different vibes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:21.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but I think this one was the most hype—or rather, it was like 150% pure positivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was so happy to perform it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:29.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And you're right, it's actually a very difficult song to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:35.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's like being at full throttle the whole time. But since Kanon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:41.30,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,loves singing so much, she's always used a handheld mic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:45.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and this time was no different. She gripped that mic tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:49.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,feeling the blue sky pushing her forward as she sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So I, Sayuri, wanted to sing while feeling like I was that blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:57.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,pushing Kanon forward from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:01.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But to do that, I had to become the blue sky myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:07.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I felt like I had to go even beyond Kanon's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:11.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I don't know if "above" or "below" is the right way to put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:17.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but I felt like I needed to have more confidence than ever to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That feeling made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:27.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Also, I ran around the stage a lot to go see everyone in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:31.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Even though it's Kanon's song,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:34.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,the lyrics use words like "we."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.30,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's not just about her; it's about "how far can we go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:42.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It felt like she was singing to you, and with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:51.23,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So I made a conscious effort to look at the audience rather than the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:51.93,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:58.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That was so much fun, it just naturally made me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was genuinely enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Like Sayuri said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,the feeling that it wasn't just about her really came across.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why everyone was cheering so loudly along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's Kanon-chan's solo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:23.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,it felt like a song for everyone, created by everyone. That sense of unity was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:27.30,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I thought, "Wow, that looks like so much fun." It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:34.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The lighting staff were so detailed too; they used marigold colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:39.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and they also used blue to represent the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was so happy they put so much thought into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:43.21,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful. It was a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was seriously so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was actually really moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The tempo of the song is basically a full-on sprint the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:02.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's not the kind of song that usually makes you feel quiet and emotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:08.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but even though it's so bright, it was somehow deeply moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Watching from backstage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Even though my solo song is totally different from Kanon-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:18.54,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It was right after your solo performance, Sayurin, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,seeing Kanon-chan's performance really gave us a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:26.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It made us feel like, "Alright, we're gonna do our best next!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It was so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Actually, Saku came up to talk to me backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I think it was during the rehearsal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:40.98,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was really nervous, wondering if I'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:45.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But Saku came over and spoke to me, and it made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,She told me she was really moved by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was moved every single time! It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.24,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was so happy. I thought, "Oh, it's Tomari-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really made my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I got a lot of energy from you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:04.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing Sayurin singing Kanon-chan's song...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I could really feel your soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:08.39,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,My soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.89,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:12.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:13.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thanks for the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad it reached you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And the costume too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Doesn't it fit perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That energetic vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:25.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Both options were good, and the other candidate was lovely too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but once it was decided, I realized this one was the perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:33.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad. The other one was like a long one-piece dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:37.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so if we'd gone with that, my movements probably would've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,a bit more graceful, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:45.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you'd sprinted full speed in that, it would've looked a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:49.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Holding the hem of the dress like a princess going up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I might have looked like I was just flailing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but it's all about the sneaker laces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Just like Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.09,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's in the lyrics of "Kokoro Kirarara" too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And these colors, blue and orange, and on the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,the "Superstar" embroidery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love that it's on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The fact that Kanon herself can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It feels like she's carrying it on her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:13.79,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:14.95,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It brings a tear to my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:19.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really feels like everyone's attention to detail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:22.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,came together to make it complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was really happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thanks for noticing all those details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.82,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Shall we move on to the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:37.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Next, we have one from Radio name: Kabocha Samurai no Hasshin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Wait, it's from Riya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.40,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I attended Day 1 of the 7th Live in Kanagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:48.44,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The visuals for 'Wild Card' on the screen matched the song perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and the costume had an Alice in Wonderland vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was completely drawn into that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:57.14,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The choreography also incorporated cards, and even though they weren't there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,it really looked like you were flipping and spreading them out."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:00.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next, we have one from Radio name: Yochi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.06,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.06,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:10.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Great job on the two days of the 7th Live in Kanagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was there at the venue for both days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.94,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Saku-chan, dressed in that cute white-based 'Wild Card' costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,your singing and dancing with perfect facial expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.12,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,was truly Tomari herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.82,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Since you mentioned the unique dance during the MC,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:30.40,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,my friends and I had a great time mimicking it on our way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you again for a wonderful live show."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.26,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.88,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.98,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,There it is, 'Wild Card'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,How was it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, since it was Tomari's first solo song,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was really, really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:55.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Plus, it had been quite a while since I'd personally
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:59.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,performed at a Liella! live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:08.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So, I was actually pretty anxious about standing on stage alone to express Tomari's character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:14.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But you know, from the very first day, during that initial 'clap-clap-clap' part,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,even though I hadn't asked anyone to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:21.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,everyone joined in. I'd hoped they would, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:25.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I didn't want to force it, so I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,In that moment, I felt this huge sense of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I realized everyone was really watching and supporting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even though I was standing on stage alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:42.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I felt like Tomari was with me and the audience was too. That feeling of not being alone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:48.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,really gave me the courage to perform with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.88,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.10,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Man, it was just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.05,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I absolutely loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.73,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:02.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The way you did your expressions, and that sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,looking down from above, like a sidelong glance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Saku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,as Tomari-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,was so good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:17.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And that outfit suited you perfectly. It was so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I have one favorite part—well, I love it all, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:24.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,after the first chorus, when you sing 'Too Cute to Handle,' 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,on the... not the Oni... the big monitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:29.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You know that big monitor in the center?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right after Saku says 'Too Cute to Handle' there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,she looks slightly to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:38.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That face is seriously so cute. I mean, it's all cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,every bit of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but while watching that, the cards... those cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:44.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,they go 'whoosh' and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,hide Tomari-chan behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:53.98,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Up until then, we're all like, 'Ah, Tomari-chan!' but then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,it's like she's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,like she's out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:02.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It just made my heart skip a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I see. So you noticed that detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.66,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,How should I put it... it's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:15.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,there's a bit of mystery, but then there's that cute 'heart' feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,like the way you sang with hearts at the end of your lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And the dance used the stairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,You had to move around, yet you kept your expressions and singing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,perfectly in character as Tomari-chan the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Aw, I'm so happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:37.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I definitely put a lot of thought into the expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I knew I couldn't just be my usual self,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so I tried not to be too bubbly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and focused on keeping a cooler vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.98,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Also, when we were learning the choreography,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,they don't usually give specific instructions for your gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:59.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, the dance teachers don't really tell you where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So I thought about it myself, and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I felt like just staring straight ahead wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:11.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I wanted to create moments where I'd look away, making people think, 'Wait, look at me!'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And then, 'Oh, she looked at me!'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:18.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I wanted to express that kind of back-and-forth teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.33,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:26.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be good, so I intentionally added more moments
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,, where I'd turn my face away. It was all calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No way, that was calculated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh man, you've totally captured my heart. This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Also, for the choreography and expression changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:43.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I changed them slightly for each performance day. I hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:47.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,that people who noticed would think, 'Oh, it's different today!'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I had that kind of thing going on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.81,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Actually, quite a lot of people noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,They'd say things like, 'Wait, wasn't that different?'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,when looking back at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,or that the timing of the glances was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You really seemed so composed and effortless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But it was seriously so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was just acting calm, but my heart was pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I really didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You deserve a huge round of applause. It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:18.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And before me... well, right before me was Pay-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:24.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sumire's song and her performance were just so overwhelming. Everyone was great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sumire had this incredible confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and Pay-chan is so talented. So, following that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,there was a lot of pressure when I went out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:38.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But I felt like looking too desperate wouldn't be very Tomari-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So I practiced as hard as I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and gave it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But watching the stream back, there are so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I wish I had done differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:55.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So if I ever get to do it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:59.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I want to raise the quality of my performance even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But it was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.88,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And that costume really suited you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What did you think of it, Saku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:14.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was so happy. You know, with "Wild Card"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:19.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,when I first heard it, it felt really dark and cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.15,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,with a bit of an alluring vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:22.69,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:27.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,when the "Behind the Spider" story came out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:36.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I realized the song was about showing a side of Tomari that had never been seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:43.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So I always felt like she wanted to show...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:43.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,that she's more than just "cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why, while the other costume was also wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and I liked it too... how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:55.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I thought if the costume had a completely different vibe from the song,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:59.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,it would be easier to express Tomari's growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:04.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I felt this one created a better contrast with the lyrics, so when it was chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:03.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was really happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really did look great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.50,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I want to see Toma wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be nice. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:20.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that everyone's been drawing illustrations of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but I hope we can see her in it officially someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:28.22,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I didn't think Tomari would ever wear an outfit that went so all-in on being cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I thought that going forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:34.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,it might not happen, so I feel like this is a new change for Tomari herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:43.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's like, because she fell in love with school idols, she can now show a side of herself she never could before, and the outfit reflects that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:42.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she got to wear something so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.54,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I want like, three of these for my house... this, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,This thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:52.67,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Like a figure! But seriously, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Just like a little figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:57.97,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And it suits her perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:58.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:04.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy they even included that playing card cat embroidery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:07.81,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The visuals on the screen were amazing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The visuals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It said "Sasaki" in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was truly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,They put so much detail into it. Thank you so much, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.54,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I want to watch just that part again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Just that part?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Well, I was watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:21.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.31,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:23.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And Tomari-chan... Sakun's expression was also very, very, very wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.01,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:31.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:32.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Time is just flying by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:34.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We have to move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.37,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next is from Liella name: K1.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:39.50,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:45.73,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Great job on the Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 7th LoveLive! Fly and High!! Music World Kanagawa performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was there to see it in person both days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:53.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The song that personally left an impression on me was the second one, "UTOPIA MAGIC."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:53.99,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:20:00.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I felt the lyrics in the chorus about "casting a spell on the usual scenery" fit the theme of this concert perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:00.69,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:09.06,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,With the different hairstyles and the new performance structure, even small changes made it feel as fresh as if I were seeing it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.68,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.34,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.12,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next, we have one from Liella name: Kubo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.02,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:15.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.90,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I attended the Liella! 7th LoveLive! Fly and High!! Music World Kanagawa performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.55,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.33,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,"UTOPIA MAGIC" was performed for the first time since the 3rd Live, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:23.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to attend the 3rd Live,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.88,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,so I was so happy I accidentally let out a shout the moment the intro started playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.45,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Aww.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:33.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it was performed on stage this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:35.88,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,the choreography for the chorus especially left a lasting impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:41.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I love the cute choreography, like making heart shapes with your hands and walking energetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:41.60,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.48,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.25,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"UTOPIA MAGIC."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We had both the low and high voices there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But man, it was great having that as the second song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:21:02.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,In recent Liella! lives, the second song has usually been something like "Let's do this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:20:59.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Songs with a lot of grit and energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:04.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:05.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.31,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Um, what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was really intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I totally didn't expect 'UTOPIA MAGIC' to come up so early,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:13.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:14.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:20.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It feels more like a song you'd save for the encore, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:18.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:20.55,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But they performed it as the second song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:28.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But it really fit the 'Music World' atmosphere perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:27.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.21,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That whole vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.05,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:34.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It had such a theme park feel to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were even saying... what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Was it like a musical?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:41.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We talked about wanting to do it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:41.47,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Like a parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:43.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:50.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were told to have the energy of parade performers, welcoming everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.15,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:53.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and to use really big, wide movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We all talked about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:22:02.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right. And since it was the second song, after doing 'Open The Gate' on the second level,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:21:59.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,we moved down for 'UTOPIA MAGIC'.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:11.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The choreography was designed to show a lot of movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:11.73,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's true for every song, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we discussed how we wanted the members' expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:21.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and movements to really come across in that second song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:29.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I wanted people to think, 'Oh, Kanon is right there!' so I used the freestyle parts to wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:27.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:29.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Kanon waves her hands really wide, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:33.81,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:42.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I thought it might be hard for characters like Tomari or Shiki to wave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:42.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It actually was pretty hard, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Those differences in expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:52.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,varied by member, so it was something we really focused on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:49.14,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:52.59,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:23:01.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We really thought about how each individual member would dance or wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:06.08,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I feel like it was a song where we really connected with our characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:06.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:11.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even the choreography was different for some members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:12.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like that part at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:13.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:14.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what was Kanon doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,During the 'dun-dun-dun-dun-dun-dun-durururu' part at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:20.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let's see... at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:24.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,after saying 'Welcome,' it was like, 'Hyah!'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:25.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Was it something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:29.04,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was pointing up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, while jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:30.75,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:34.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Tomari is actually hilarious right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:32.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:34.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What does Tomari do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:35.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right there, at that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Tomari is doing a jellyfish move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:39.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I don't think I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I talked with the dance teacher like, 'What should Tomari do here?'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:50.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone else was doing movements that felt like their characters, but we wondered what Tomari's would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:47.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:47.83,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:53.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But since this song...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:24:02.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,is so cute and catchy, we thought instead of her usual cool and sharp self,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:58.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:04.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,maybe we should make her look a little cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:05.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love that! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So we decided on this... jellyfish move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's way more of a jellyfish than I expected, now that I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:12.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.90,0:24:17.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone has noticed it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:18.53,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,at least from what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.53,0:24:19.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:20.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was really funny, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:24.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But, you know, Tomari-chan... how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:29.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She has these surprisingly humorous expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:28.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Exactly, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:40.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She's probably being serious and doesn't mean to be funny, but from an outsider's perspective, it's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:36.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.15,0:24:39.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.84,0:24:42.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really makes me think she's her sister's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:44.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah, right. They really are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.68,0:24:45.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.26,0:24:46.07,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The blood connection is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.07,0:24:46.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:48.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She's a bit of a natural in what she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:53.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Watching her is so unpredictable, which makes it really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:52.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:54.67,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.67,0:24:55.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:57.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So she was doing a jellyfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.38,0:24:57.97,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.97,0:24:58.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:25:12.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,While doing that choreography, I wondered what kind of faces everyone had, so I looked at the people in the front, but no one looked confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.36,0:25:15.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They were all just smiling at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.04,0:25:18.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see. Maybe they were under the spell of UTOPIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.32,0:25:18.93,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Maybe they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:20.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Maybe they didn't even realize it was a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.82,0:25:22.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Apparently, that part was a jellyfish, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.85,0:25:23.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.62,0:25:24.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It was a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:28.34,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's such a fun song, I hope we can perform it again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.34,0:25:29.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.28,0:25:30.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:33.48,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Anyway, thank you everyone for all the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:35.06,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Comment: 0,0:25:35.06,0:25:37.24,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Lunchtime Request ===
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.06,0:25:37.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now, let's play a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.24,0:25:42.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're going to play the song we just talked about, "UTOPIA MAGIC."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.68,0:25:43.27,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.27,0:25:43.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.88,0:25:44.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.92,0:25:48.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please fall under the spell of "UTOPIA MAGIC" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.60,0:25:49.11,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:52.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Now, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.38,0:25:53.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,By Liella!,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:54.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,"UTOPIA MAGIC."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:26:05.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,There's no real meaning, but I'm having fun waving at the contrails.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.24,0:26:15.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,After laying out a picnic sheet, the rooftop where I sing with you is UTOPIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.72,0:26:20.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah, the wind slipping through the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.32,0:26:24.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Catch it now, even that sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:27.17,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It feels like I could fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:32.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Casting a spell on the usual scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.68,0:26:36.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Your smile gives me happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.79,0:26:38.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.48,0:26:47.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If I say "I love you" out loud, everywhere becomes the most wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.52,0:26:54.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Please stay by my side forever from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.80,0:26:58.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.80,0:27:15.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I can touch it as many times as I want, so let's hold our breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.61,0:27:17.11,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.88,0:27:18.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,on the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.44,0:27:23.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The scenery is looking all fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.24,0:27:27.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Basking in the sunlight with a dazed feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:33.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,my precious treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.99,0:27:35.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,keep increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.48,0:27:40.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you're here, even the future will shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.84,0:27:50.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This is the most wonderful place, enough to make me forget time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.48,0:27:57.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let those fingers stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.72,0:28:15.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Lunchtime Broadcast Station, Lieraji.
Comment: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:23.96,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Closing ===
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:23.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Announcements from Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:28.45,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,First, regarding music information, we have some brand new news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.45,0:28:29.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.28,0:28:33.73,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We will be releasing a new single on Wednesday, June 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.73,0:28:34.25,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.17,0:28:35.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.77,0:28:36.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:37.23,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:43.72,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Yes, this single is scheduled to include one new song and its off-vocal version, for a total of two tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.72,0:28:47.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Details will be announced at a later date, so please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:54.10,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next, on Wednesday, July 8th, we will release the "Liella to Musubu Project" mini-album.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.10,0:29:02.44,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This will be released in five versions: Original, Photo, Team Kodomo, Team Sports, and Team Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:10.06,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Original, Team Kodomo, Team Sports, and Team Midori versions will feature new illustrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.06,0:29:13.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,while the Photo version will feature new photos of the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.96,0:29:22.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This mini-album is scheduled to include four songs, including one new group song, plus their off-vocal versions for a total of eight tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Also, all versions will include an advance lottery application ticket for the Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.96,0:29:31.24,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and Love Live! Superstar!!.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.84,0:29:35.90,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Additionally, as a first-press bonus, the Original, Team Kodomo,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.90,0:29:39.02,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Team Sports, and Team Midori versions will include stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.02,0:29:41.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Photo version will include purikura-style stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.32,0:29:46.70,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Furthermore, as a bundle purchase bonus, you'll receive a Liella! sticker book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.70,0:29:48.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.88,0:29:55.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And to celebrate the release of the "Liella to Musubu Project" mini-album, we've decided to hold a handover event.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:55.87,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:30:00.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The dates are Friday, October 2nd and Friday, October 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.36,0:30:04.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Those who pre-order or purchase the mini-album at participating stores
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:07.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,will be invited to the handover event via a lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.44,0:30:13.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The cast members will vary by date, so please check the application requirements
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.60,0:30:14.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,before applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:18.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please check the Love Live! Superstar!! official website for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.28,0:30:21.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next is an announcement from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.48,0:30:26.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Start Deck "Love Live! Superstar!!" featuring only Liella! members and songs is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:50.22,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The latest information will be posted on the Loveca official website and official X account,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.22,0:30:51.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so please keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.04,0:30:53.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now for appearance information.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.16,0:30:57.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Starting April 1st, Season 2 of "Liella no Tutorial" will begin on Nippon TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.60,0:31:02.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Time Machine 3-go will continue as the program MCs from Season 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.52,0:31:07.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and Nittele TADA after the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.80,0:31:08.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.60,0:31:16.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Furthermore, a live event to commemorate the broadcast, "Love Live! Superstar!! Liella no Tutoria-Live 2026," will be held on August 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.78,0:31:19.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and 2nd at LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.32,0:31:27.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Official advance lottery applications are currently open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, March 22nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.84,0:31:29.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please check this out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.12,0:31:35.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,For details on all the information announced today, please check the official Liella! X account
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.20,0:31:38.90,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,or the Love Live! Superstar!! official website.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.90,0:31:40.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's all for the announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:56.30,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye to Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Lunchtime Broadcast Station, Lieraji.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.30,0:31:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're always looking for your emails here at Lieraji.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.64,0:32:03.70,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're currently accepting thoughts on our songs, the TV anime, and our live concerts,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.70,0:32:07.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,as well as general mail like messages and questions for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.28,0:32:11.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We also have "Hamburg is Agree," where you share your little favorites,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.60,0:32:16.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and "Lunchtime Request," where you request Liella! songs to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.08,0:32:19.54,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Finally, there's "Open the Gate, Ouen the Yell,"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:23.00,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,where we give you a push when you need some support.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:24.72,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're waiting for lots of emails!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:27.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And now, here's the info for the next broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.08,0:32:35.45,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Episode 265, airing next Tuesday, March 24th, will feature Yabushima Akane, the voice of Mei Yoneme, as our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.45,0:32:36.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.20,0:32:40.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, we talked a lot today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:40.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,how was it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.84,0:32:41.95,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Man, it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.95,0:32:42.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:43.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:44.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Not enough at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.28,0:32:45.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Look, I still have so much left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.68,0:32:46.25,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.25,0:32:47.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Because there's just so much to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.72,0:32:48.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:50.44,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.20,0:32:53.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Can we keep talking next week? I wonder if we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.24,0:32:56.34,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It looks like we'll be able to talk more next week too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:57.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Then let's talk then!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.51,0:32:58.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:32:58.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.76,0:33:02.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll just keep talking about our 7th Live impressions forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.56,0:33:04.25,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I honestly want to talk about it for the next three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.25,0:33:04.77,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.32,0:33:06.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The things we want to say about the live just keep piling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.76,0:33:10.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Everything ends up being about the 7th Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.52,0:33:12.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,If we don't do Lieraji every single day, it might not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:13.77,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let's do it every day then!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.77,0:33:14.34,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:15.07,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.07,0:33:15.85,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.85,0:33:16.90,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're doing it every day now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.90,0:33:17.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Send us your mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:18.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.11,0:33:20.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.62,0:33:21.19,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.19,0:33:21.87,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.87,0:33:23.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please tune in next week too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.30,0:33:23.83,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.64,0:33:29.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's all for this episode of Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Lieraji.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.04,0:33:31.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri, the voice of Kanon Shibuya,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.72,0:33:33.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Tomari Onitsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:34.91,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.36,0:33:37.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.96,0:33:41.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Time and heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:47.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,are creatures that know no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:48.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,In the twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.04,0:34:06.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Lieraji.
